summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed to the City of Seattle executed on February 22, 1909, by Frank W. Brigham and Mary E. Brigham, his wife; W. K. Cameron and Mary Cameron, his wife; M. A. Renashaw and Hattie Renshaw his wife; H. H. Benton and Mary M. Benton, his wife, for a part of Section 9, Township 25 North, Range 4 East.
